::Starscream all of a sudden got the feeling that someone was behind him.  he 
turned around, but it was too late.  He got hit head on by the chaochitan 
energy.  In a last ditch effort to be saved, he opened his comm on an all 
Pack Predacon frequency::
Starscream: Th- this is Starscream. I've been damaged heavily by an unknown 
bot.  Please c-come and h-help. My coordinates are(he gives his coordinates).
::he cloeses his comm and falls into stasis lock::
